trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.QuotaControl" /> class is used to pass the security identifier (SID) of a security principle to retrieve quota-related data.
trans-unit.target: A classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.QuotaControl" /> é usada para passar a SID (identificador de segurança) de um princípio de segurança para recuperar dados relacionados à cota.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.QuotaControl.#ctor" /> constructor creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.QuotaControl" /> class.
trans-unit.target: O construtor <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.QuotaControl.#ctor" /> cria uma instância da classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.QuotaControl" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.QuotaControl.#ctor" /> constructor creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.QuotaControl" /> class.
trans-unit.target: O construtor <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.QuotaControl.#ctor" /> cria uma instância da classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.QuotaControl" />.

trans-unit.source: The SID of the security principle.
trans-unit.target: A SID do princípio de segurança.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.QuotaControl.#ctor(System.Security.Principal.SecurityIdentifier)" /> constructor creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.QuotaControl" /> class using the specified SID.
trans-unit.target: O construtor <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.QuotaControl.#ctor(System.Security.Principal.SecurityIdentifier)" /> cria uma instância da classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.QuotaControl" /> usando a SID especificada.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.QuotaControl.GetValue" /> method returns the SID associated with this query.
trans-unit.target: O método <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.QuotaControl.GetValue" /> retorna a SID associada a esta consulta.

trans-unit.source: The SID associated with this query.
trans-unit.target: A SID associada a esta consulta.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.QuotaControl.QuerySid" /> property contains the SID of the security principle.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.QuotaControl.QuerySid" /> contém a SID do princípio de segurança.

trans-unit.source: The SID of the security principle.
trans-unit.target: A SID do princípio de segurança.
